[26/04/2019 15:32:10] <font color="#ffffff">"Anem a pescar".</font>
[26/04/2019 15:32:10] <font color="#ffffff">Si no, "anem a chorrar".</font>
[26/04/2019 15:32:11] <font color="#ffffff">"Anem a churrá".</font>
